          <li><a href="http://www.iotasupport.com/whatisiota.shtml">iotasupport</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://www.tangleblog.com/what-is-iota-what-is-the-tangle/">tangleblog</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://www.tangleblog.com/2017/06/05/ama-answers-for-newcomers/">tangleblog faq</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
