        <h4 class="panel-title">
          <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse12">Should I re-attach or make the transaction again?</a>
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div id="collapse12" class="panel-collapse collapse">
        <div class="panel-body">
          By opening the transaction, one of the following will be true:
          <ul>
            <li>You see a green re-attach button. It is only visible if we recommend you to replay</li>
            <li>You get a red warning telling you that the transaction is a double spend. In that case you might have to do the transaction again manually</li>
            <li>You don't get any particular instruction. In this case you should neither re-attach or resend.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
